title: Application complete
successParagraph1: Your application will be processed as soon as the Civil Enforcement Registry receives your documents.
successParagraph2: You will receive the grant of cet and any copies you’ve ordered within 20 working days of your documents being received.
successParagraph3: We’ll email you if we need any more information. You can also call the Civil Enforcement Registry on {helpLineNumber} if you have any questions.
